data.description: This well-maintained home features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths with 1,337 square feet, installed hurricane shutters all around the home, and solar panels! Your living room is spacious and has a beautiful fireplace. Walk into your kitchen and love all the cabinet space with stainless steel appliances included and your laundry room is already complete with stackable washer and dryer! Your primary bedroom has a nice size closet and French doors that open up to your bathroom which comes complete with a large tub and stand-up shower. Both spare bedrooms are generously sized as well! Your backyard is entertainment ready with a large patio space, storage shed, and home has a new AC unit! Move in ready! Motivated Seller bring all offers!
